{"title":"bug引题-学习Junit和Junit.Jupiter.api区别","uid":"ed80e4e3f3e8382b0b8f5e494dcfbbef","slug":"Junit去呗","date":"2023-12-15T14:42:14.000Z","updated":"2023-12-15T14:58:08.284Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Junit去呗.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"Junit和Junit-Jupiter-api用法区别\"><a href=\"#Junit和Junit-Jupiter-api用法区别\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Junit和Junit.Jupiter.api用法区别\"></a>Junit和Junit.Jupiter.api用法区别</h1><blockquote>\n<p>Junit 5 &#x3D; Junit Platform + Junit Jupiter + Junit Vintage</p>\n<p>Junit4中的@Test是import org.junit.Test;<br>Jupiter中的@Test是import org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"1-bug引题\"><a href=\"#1-bug引题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. bug引题\"></a>1. bug引题</h2><ol>\n<li><p>今天在学习Spring的时候，整合Spring5-text5测试环境的时候</p>\n<p>@Autowired 一直提示是空指针，搞得我很困惑，@Component没有问题，配置类也没有问题</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">@SpringJUnitConfig(value = &#123;testProtoxy.class&#125;)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title class_\">testioc</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"meta\">@Autowired</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">public</span> Calculator calculator;      <span class=\"comment\">//有接口用接口取</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"meta\">@Test</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title function_\">testioc01</span><span class=\"params\">()</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"variable\">add</span> <span class=\"operator\">=</span> calculator.add(<span class=\"number\">1</span>, <span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        System.out.println(<span class=\"string\">&quot;add = &quot;</span> + add);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><p>后来百度之后，发现在测试函数上面加一句即可正常运行</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">@RunWith(SpringJUnit4ClassRunner.class)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>当然还没有学习到太深，只是靠字面理解这不就是跑在junit4的环境下面吗，那我的依赖</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;dependency&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;groupId&gt;org.junit.jupiter&lt;/groupId&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;artifactId&gt;junit-jupiter-api&lt;/artifactId&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;version&gt;5.3.1&lt;/version&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/dependency&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>岂不是白白声明到5了</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>我就想起去百度这两个有什么区别的时候，遂产生了此篇记录博客</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"2-学习区别\"><a href=\"#2-学习区别\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 学习区别\"></a>2. 学习区别</h2><p>Junit 5 &#x3D; Junit Platform + Junit Jupiter + Junit Vintage</p>\n<p>Junit4中的@Test是import org.junit.Test;<br>Jupiter中的@Test是import org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312152251520.png\" alt=\"image-20231215225144324\"></p>\n<p>在测试类中@Test导入了****Junit.Jupiter.api****的Class文件后，我们就不需要再加上@RunWith注解了</p>\n<p>否则在junit4下，需要如下配置</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">@RunWith(SpringJUnit4ClassRunner.class)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">@SpringJUnitConfig(value = &#123;testProtoxy.class, javaProtoxy.class&#125;)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","text":"Junit和Junit.Jupiter.api用法区别 Junit 5 &#x3D; Junit Platform + Junit Jupiter + Juni...","permalink":"/post/Junit去呗","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.3k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":11,"path":"api/categories/Java.json"},{"name":"Spring","slug":"Java/Spring","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Java/Spring.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Learn","slug":"Learn","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Learn.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Junit%E5%92%8CJunit-Jupiter-api%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Junit和Junit.Jupiter.api用法区别</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-bug%E5%BC%95%E9%A2%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1. bug引题</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2. 学习区别</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"CYLIN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312241427715.jpg","link":"/","description":"多读书多看报，少吃零食多睡觉","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":